Title: Login Test
Preconditions: User is on the login page
Steps: 1. Enter username\n2. Enter password\n3. Click on login button

Title: Search Test
Steps: 1. Enter search term in search bar\n2. Click on search button

Title: Compatibility Test
Steps: 1. Navigate to website\n2. Click on different links
Expected Results: Website functions correctly without any errors

Title: Negative Test
Preconditions: User is on the login page
Steps: 1. Enter incorrect username\n2. Enter incorrect password\n3. Click on login button
